{"tid":1306702,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚想讀fashion嘅同學仔!!!","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:08:38.000Z","uid":197081,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1aef56195b45f017b78e0043468489df0b0e4d2","tid":1306702,"uid":197081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:58:27.000Z","msg":"想讀Fashion 嘅你，揀咗科未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDSE只要有22222（包中、英文）, 就可以入讀由OU同Cita (製衣業訓練局)舉辦嘅 Digital Fashion Creation 數碼時裝設計高級文憑課程。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />減左政府資助之後，學費每年HK$23,000。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成呢個課程之後, 有機會銜接去Poly 或者OU嘅degree。<br />\n<br />\n咁報讀有咩優勢呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />服裝設計師創意多，但每次時裝設計改動，都要做辦出來，就會費時失事。而家，好多服裝公司都開始用3Ｄ Fashion Design CAD軟件嚟做開發。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除了學識不同的數碼軟件，掌握時尚產品開發和服裝設計過程，而且可以在服裝公司實習。仲可以最快四年內獲得學位資歷！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以呢個課程對你嘅未來响服裝行業發展好有幫助，而家好多院校都未有此專業範疇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知多Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\nWhatsapp可以搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<a href=\"https://wa.me/85259302906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwa.me%2F85259302906&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8521m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=1617fa15\" target=\"_blank\">https://w